  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n\r\n*Summary*: This problem will occur with any app which uses github for authentication. For exmaple: I am trying to login to https://openbounty.status.im:444 via Status app using `@browse` and seems in fact I need to login twice.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nI can login from the first attempt\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nI need to login twice\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Go to Browse\r\n- Type https://openbounty.status.im:444 and proceed with the authorization through Github\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: last seen in `0.9.12-1-g7256ddaf+ (1872)`\r\n* Operating System: Android\r\n\r\n#### Logs\r\n* TF: https://app.testfairy.com/projects/4803622-status/builds/6964718/sessions/63/?accessToken=DKDOpgroWAGhBLpE6Tj-wnDHN2c from 1:55\r\n",
